{"title":"整理Windows桌面右键菜单","uid":"fc1054d578289a25829717105df4941c","slug":"整理Windows桌面右键菜单","date":"2022-03-23T11:54:01.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:51.823Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/整理Windows桌面右键菜单.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/windows-6210803_1920.jpg"],"content":"<p>强迫症福音，整理自己的Windows桌面菜单！</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323200043532.png\" alt = \"上图看效果\"/>\n</div>\n\n<h1 id=\"基础操作\"><a href=\"#基础操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础操作\"></a>基础操作</h1><p>直接用火绒安全（<a href=\"https://murphyhoucn.github.io/2022/01/24/Windows%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%95/\">Windows端个人常用软件清单</a>中推荐过）设置一些功能的开或者不开！</p>\n<p>火绒官网：<a href=\"https://www.huorong.cn/\">火绒安全 (huorong.cn)</a></p>\n<p>比如，我把Git Bash和Git GUI都关了，所有的命令行操作都使用Windows Terminal（<a href=\"https://murphyhoucn.github.io/2022/01/24/Windows%E7%AB%AF%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%95/\">Windows端个人常用软件清单</a>中推荐过，强烈推荐！）</p>\n<div align = \"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323200249135.png\">\n</div>\n\n<h1 id=\"删除和添加新建选项\"><a href=\"#删除和添加新建选项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除和添加新建选项\"></a>删除和添加新建选项</h1><h2 id=\"删除\"><a href=\"#删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除\"></a>删除</h2><p>使用regedit管理注册表可以实现，但是我觉得还是有些麻烦，涉及到权限问题，这里推荐一个小工具——ShellMenuNew</p>\n<p>下载地址：<a href=\"https://www.nirsoft.net/utils/shell_menu_new.html\">ShellMenuNew - Disable/enable ‘New’ menu items in Windows Explorer (nirsoft.net)</a></p>\n<p>下载得到的压缩包解压后直接可以使用，汉化的话可以在该网页直接下载汉化包，结压之后直接放在文件目录下，重启软件即可获得汉化后的应用。</p>\n<div align = \"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323202227547.png\"/>\n</div>\n<div align = \"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323202328611.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"新建\"><a href=\"#新建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建\"></a>新建</h2><p>参考资料:<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/viptung/article/details/79188540\">windows右键菜单添加新建Python文件选项（可设置模板）_Ryan.D的博客-CSDN博客_右键新建py</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>找个文件夹建立一个模板文件（可以写一个README记录一下这些文件是干什么用的，防止以后误删除！）</li>\n</ol>\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323202900284.png\">\n</div>\n2. Win+r，输入regedit，进入编辑注册表\n\n<p>进入如下地址，<code>计算机\\HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT\\.py</code>，修改什么后缀文件就进入那个后缀的编辑页面。</p>\n<p>新建一个<code>项</code>,命名为<code>ShellNew</code></p>\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323203146020.png\"/>\n</div>\n3. 新建一个`字符串值`命名为`FileName`\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323203500964.png\"/>\n</div>\n4. 对`FileName`右键修改\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323203622053.png\"/>\n</div>\n将数值修改为**模板文件**的**绝对路径**\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323203744509.png\"/>\n</div>\n5. 重复上述操作可以讲其他类型的文件一并加入我新建列表中！\n\n<h1 id=\"新建项排序\"><a href=\"#新建项排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建项排序\"></a>新建项排序</h1><p>参考资料：<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/0648378a2bdd\">01 调整Win10桌面右键新建顺序 - 简书 (jianshu.com)</a></p>\n<p><code>计算机\\HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\Discardable\\PostSetup\\ShellNew</code></p>\n<ol>\n<li>修改自己的文件排序<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323204351881.png\"/>\n</div></li>\n<li>设置权限<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323204451581.png\"/>\n</div></li>\n</ol>\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323204552500.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div align = \"center\">\n<img src=\"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/image-20220323204707017.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n<p>完成！</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"强迫症福音，整理自己的Windows桌面菜单！ 基础操作直接用火绒安全（Windows端个人常用软件清单中推荐过）设置一些功能的开或者不开！ 火绒官网：火绒安全 (huorong.cn) 比如，我把Git Bash和Git GUI都关了，所有的命令行操作都使用Windows Te...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":944,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"工具利器","slug":"工具利器","count":7,"path":"api/categories/工具利器.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"桌面整理","slug":"桌面整理","count":1,"path":"api/tags/桌面整理.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基础操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%92%8C%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除和添加新建选项</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新建</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新建项排序</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"记一次上云经历","uid":"2e60e32c8ceaea3828a8b54c6c941cef","slug":"记一次上云经历","date":"2